# Flutter Client Only

- For mobile app changes, work only in `client/mia_companion/`.
- Do not modify React Native files in `client/mia_react_native/`.
- Do not modify native Android files in `client/mia_android/`.
- Only touch React Native or native Android if the user explicitly asks for those clients in the current request.
